prisma_schema:
model ChatMessage {
  id              Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  text            String
  parentMessageId String?
  createdAt       DateTime @default(now())
  chatId          BigInt
}

model History {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  uuid      BigInt    @unique
  title     String
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime?
}

model Prompt {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  prompt    String
  title     String
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime?
}
